<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> إِخْلَاصُ الْعِبَادَةِ للهِ تَعَالَى، وَبَذْلُ الْجُهْدِ فِي تَحْسِينِهَا وَإِكْمَالِهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> مَعِيَّةُ اللهِ الْخَاصَّةُ بِالْمُحْسِنِينَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> الْفَوْزُ بِالْجَنَّةِ وَرُؤْيَةِ اللهِ تَعَالَى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>